name: Baked Car I
description:
Had a car crash accident for the very first time in my life six years ago. Got our car repaired and repainted in this big car workshop. I was so fascinated by the whole process and surroundings as it was, too, my first time experiencing such sightings.

Captured and edited with my 2015 ASUS Zenfone 4 - A400CG Android phone.
